cast.overview: Set high atop snow-capped mountains in the adrenaline-fueled world of competitive snowboarding, the Disney Channel Original Movie “Cloud 9″ tells the inspiring story of two snowboarders who must overcome self-doubt to learn that achieving their dreams is possible.
cast.title: Cloud 9

details.biography:
Amy Farrington is an American actress and former model, best known for her role as Stacey Devers on The Michael Richards Show and as Lt. Detective Piper Lynch in the CBS drama series S.W.A.T..

She's also had recurring roles on The New Adventures of Old Christine and Faking It.
details.name: Amy Farrington
